.Sh NAME
.Nm modem
.Nd fixed baud rate wrapper
.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl r Ar rate
.Ar command ...
.
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
runs the
.Ar command
in a new PTY
with a fixed baud rate.
.
.Pp
The arguments are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl r Ar rate
Set the baud rate.
The default is 19200.
.El
.
.Sh BUGS
Window size changes are not propagated
to the child PTY.
